original_title: Princess Diana: Her Life in Jewels
overview: From fairy-tale wedding to tragic funeral, the extraordinary life of Diana, Princess of Wales, was a chronicle of jewels, each marking distinct junctures in her life. Beginning with the infamous sapphire engagement ring, Diana was showered with gems each of which held a unique significance to the current events in her life. This revealing program follows the stories of Diana's most famous gems.
title: Princess Diana: Her Life in Jewels
